quran[13]{c,v,t}:
  44,30,Dájúdájú A gba àwọn ọmọ ’Isrọ̄’īl là nínú ìyà yẹpẹrẹ
  44,31,(A là wọ́n) lọ́wọ́ Fir‘aon. Dájúdájú ó jẹ́ onígbèéraga. Ó sì wà nínú àwọn alákọyọ
  44,32,A kúkú ṣà wọ́n lẹ́ṣà lórí àwọn ẹ̀dá (àsìkò tiwọn) pẹ̀lú ìmọ̀
  44,33,A sì fún wọn ní àwọn àmì tí àdánwò pọ́nńbélé wà nínú rẹ̀
  44,34,Dájúdájú àwọn wọ̀nyí ń wí pé
  44,35,Kò sí ikú kan àyàfi ikú àkọ́kọ́ (tí ó pa wá nílé ayé). Wọn kò sì níí gbé wa dìde
  44,36,"(Bí bẹ́ẹ̀ kọ́), ẹ mú àwọn bàbá wa wá tí ẹ bá jẹ́ olódodo"
  44,37,Ṣé àwọn ni wọ́n lóore jùlọ ni tàbí àwọn ènìyàn Tubba‘u àti àwọn t’ó ṣíwájú wọn? A pa wọ́n rẹ́; dájúdájú wọ́n jẹ́ ẹlẹ́ṣẹ̀
  44,38,"A kò ṣẹ̀dá àwọn sánmọ̀, ilẹ̀ àti ohunkóhun tí ń bẹ láààrin méjèèjì pẹ̀lú eré ṣíṣe"
  44,39,"A kò dá àwọn méjèèjì bí kò ṣe pẹ̀lú òdodo, ṣùgbọ́n ọ̀pọ̀lọ́pọ̀ wọn ni kò mọ̀"
  44,40,"Dájúdájú ọjọ́ òpínyà (ìyẹn, ọjọ́ àjíǹde) ni àkókò àdéhùn fún gbogbo wọn pátápátá"
  44,41,Ní ọjọ́ tí ọ̀rẹ́ kan kò níí fi kiní kan rọ ọ̀rẹ́ kan lọ́rọ̀. A ò sì níí ràn wọ́n lọ́wọ́
  44,42,"Àyàfi ẹni tí Allāhu bá kẹ́. Dájúdájú Allāhu, Òun ni Alágbára, Àṣàkẹ́-ọ̀run"